{"tid":2258781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「擁核大國都沒參加」　日本質疑《禁止核武器條約》效力　重申不加入","createTime":"2020-10-26T10:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T15:30:14.000Z","uid":75656,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3c844db1f4c0ee21020e6c869ead19bd475362","tid":2258781,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:12:50.000Z","msg":"岸信夫昨天在山口市舉行記者會時表示「擁核國都不參加的條約，不得不對其有效性感到懷疑」。<br />\n<br />\n岸信夫說，日本是唯一曾被原子彈轟炸的國家，一定要領導各國廢除核子武器。其中重要的是，包含擁核國在內的世界各國，需具體表態廢除核武、必須要創造國際社會能達成共識的環境。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府發言人、內閣官房長官加藤勝信今天重申日本不會簽署「禁止核武器條約」。<br />\n<br />\n加藤表示，<span class=\"red\">條約廢除核武的目標與日本一致，但要維持、強化嚇阻的能力，適當對應安保威脅的同時，踏實且現實地追求縮減核武，才是適當做法。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201026/5XUXGTQKEBAXTOVTEEWN2YK4NQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201026%2F5XUXGTQKEBAXTOVTEEWN2YK4NQ%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=346b660c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201026%2F5XUXGTQKEBAXTOVTEEWN2YK4NQ%2F&h=7db09b9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201026/5XUXGTQKEBAXTOVTEEWN2YK4NQ/</a>"},{"pid":"838b5079613237b3cd40f3e4fc990d597f02eed9","tid":2258781,"uid":253016,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:18:30.000Z","msg":"講經咩 國際公約同垃圾冇分別"},{"pid":"773d4a3ae6638f6ab2f1189ad3abd9244c03df47","tid":2258781,"uid":152944,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"真心一問 二戰日本俾美國炸 戰後泡沫經濟又俾美國玩 點解日本仲可以同美國咁friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f054fd884da6f956c1f4e7961877db7506c18186","tid":2258781,"uid":257680,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"773d4a3ae6638f6ab2f1189ad3abd9244c03df47","tid":2258781,"uid":152944,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"真心一問 二戰日本俾美